Emil Design ‚Äì Furniture with personality and quality, designed just for you.

Custom Furniture Manufacturing
We specialize in custom furniture manufacturing, creating unique pieces tailored to your specific needs and preferences. Our skilled craftsmen meticulously craft each piece, paying attention to every detail to ensure high-quality and exquisite furniture that perfectly matches your vision. Whether you're looking for bespoke sofas, tables, chairs, or cabinets, we have the expertise to bring your custom furniture ideas to life.

Reliable Delivery Service with Guarantee
Along with reliable delivery, we guarantee a professional and secure service. Our dedicated delivery team is experienced and efficient, handling the transportation of your furniture with care and reliability. We assure you that your furniture will arrive at its destination in the best possible condition and within the agreed timeframe. We utilize well-equipped vehicles and take necessary precautions to prevent any damage or breakage.

Assembly according to Individual Projects
We offer assembly services tailored to your individual projects. Our skilled team is proficient in assembling various types of furniture, including complex and customized designs. Whether it's modular furniture, shelving units, or intricate pieces, we have the expertise to assemble them accurately and efficiently. We pay attention to every detail to ensure a seamless and sturdy assembly that meets your specific requirements.

Furniture Repair and Refurbishment
We provide furniture repair and refurbishment services to restore the beauty and functionality of your beloved furniture pieces. Our experienced craftsmen can fix damaged furniture, replace worn-out parts, and refinish surfaces to breathe new life into your cherished items. From minor repairs to complete furniture restoration, we offer comprehensive solutions to make your furniture look as good as new.

Furniture Made by Us
When you choose our furniture, you can trust that it is manufactured by us. We take pride in producing our own furniture, ensuring the highest standards of quality and craftsmanship. By controlling the entire manufacturing process, from design to production, we guarantee that each piece meets our strict quality guidelines. With our furniture, you can enjoy the assurance of exceptional craftsmanship and durable materials.

Hanging lamps: Hanging lamps are suspended from the ceiling and provide overhead lighting with style. They come in various designs, sizes, and materials, and are a great way to add ambient lighting and a decorative element to any room.
column9: light,lamp,hanging lamp

column6: Standing lamps: Standing lamps, also known as floor lamps, are freestanding lighting fixtures that can be easily placed in any corner of a room. They provide both ambient and task lighting and come in a variety of styles, including tripod, arc, and torchiere, allowing you to enhance the overall lighting scheme and add a touch of elegance to your space.

Table lamps: Table lamps are versatile lighting options that can be placed on bedside tables, desks, or side tables. They provide localized lighting for reading, working, or creating a cozy atmosphere. With a wide range of designs, sizes, and shade options available, table lamps offer both functionality and aesthetic appeal.

Wall light: Wall lights, also known as sconces, are fixtures installed on the walls to provide focused or ambient lighting. They can be used as decorative accents or functional lighting sources, adding a touch of elegance and sophistication to hallways, living rooms, bedrooms, or outdoor spaces.

Outdoor lighting: Outdoor lighting includes various fixtures designed specifically for exterior spaces. These can include wall-mounted lights, pathway lights, garden lights, and floodlights. Outdoor lighting not only enhances the aesthetic appeal of your outdoor areas but also provides safety and security by illuminating walkways, entrances, and outdoor living spaces.
